OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FStaying
OL,6,Fdry, sunny and very warm throughout.
OL,7,FAn increased breeze may allow things
OL,8,Fto feel slightly cooler at times.
OL,9,FNights remaining warm.
